Louis Greco
Vice President & National Sales Desk Manager
Louis Greco serves as Vice President – National Sales Desk Manager for CION Securities, LLC.  Since joining the firm in 2015, Louis has served in multiple capacities and has covered several territories as an internal sales specialist, including New England, the Mid-Atlantic and Southeast regions. Mr. Greco came to CION with various sales-experience, working prior at AllianceBernstein, LP as well as Automatic Data Processing (ADP, Inc.) 
While at ADP, Louis began his career in sales by partnering and supporting small-to-middle-market US companies (1-500 employees) throughout the United States to implement advantageous tax-strategies by means of Corporate 401(k) and SIMPLE IRA plan sales. Subsequent to his time at ADP, Louis also worked at AllianceBernstein where he covered the Mid-Atlantic, Midwest, New England and Southeast regions of the US in various channels, including: Defined Benefit and Defined Contribution Investment-Only, Sub-Advisory/Insurance and US Retail. 
In addition to his role as National Sales Desk Manager, Louis contributes to a number of firm-wide initiatives such as business-development, research & marketing and the training and on-boarding of new-hires.
