Ares Co-Founders, Anthony Ressler and Michael Arougheti, discuss Ares’ expertise and investment capabilities across different asset classes.  Ares is one of the largest global alternative asset managers, with three complementary and market leading investment groups—Credit, Private Equity and Real Estate--that offer a broad range of flexible investment solutions along the risk reward spectrum.  Ares leverages relationships, sector knowledge and industry insights across its broad platform to source and evaluate investment.

